    :noteText "Charter Mapping: Art 47 Right to effective remedy" .


:HE050 rdf:type :Obligation ;
    :requirementID "HE050" ;
    :requirementText "Have you considered whether your AI system could be misused or diverted from its original purpose (function creep)?" ;
